caption: {'text': 'Today is the Non-Profit Connections Virtual Career Fair! Thank you to all of the organizations participating. Students: make sure to register for the fair on Handshake.'}

author: heinzcollege_careersvcs
caption:
{'text': 'HAPPENING TODAY!

Social Good through Public Finance and Wealth Management
Friday, March 12th
12-1pm ET
Register via Handshake

Join us for a candid conversation with MSPPM alums Jenai Booker and Shawneil Campbell, from the class of 2015. In this conversation they aim to do three things: (1) Demystify preconceived notions about the fields of Public Finance and Wealth Management; (2) Illustrate how to get the most out of your MSPPM degree; and (3) Network with all of you. We look forward to a fruitful conversation.'}

author: heinzcollege_careersvcs
caption: {'text': 'Today kicks off the @heinzcollege Washington DC Colloquium! The Washington DC Colloquium is an annual Heinz College event that aims to educate students on different industries and sectors in Washington DC, while engaging with our Heinz College alumni network.'}

author: heinzcollege_careersvcs
caption: {'text': 'Network Nationally continues today! Register and log in to the event to live chat with over 40 alumni from all degree programs hosting virtual booths. Thanks to all the Alumni, Students, and Staff that make these events possible!'}

author: heinzcollege_careersvcs
caption:
{'text': 'Calling all Heinz College of Information Systems and Public Policy Alumni & Students!

Virtually meet and network with alumni from various industry sectors all around the country.  Alumni will host virtual booths in the InfernoAR platform and will represent all of the various Heinz Programs. Join a live chat by reviewing the schedule and the booth information that includes alumni names, programs, graduation years, job titles, current company and brief bios.
Once you are logged into Network Nationally you will also have the opportunity for real time text chats taking place among all Event Attendees who jump in on Thursday & Friday so be sure to create an Attendee Profile to participate!

‚Ä¢ Register for Network Nationally: link on Facebook
‚Ä¢ Please complete a Profile so you show up as an event Attendee

author: heinzcollege_careersvcs
caption: {'text': 'Destinations in Data - happening THIS WEEK! \nA three-day virtual event for @heinzcollege students to learn how Data Analytics skills can be applied in various industries such as Technology, E-commerce, Healthcare, Public Tech, & Entertainment. Attendees will have the opportunity to establish current Heinz College student connections by visiting virtual student showcase booths, hear from Heinz alumni and industry leaders, and see corporate recruiters who want to hire Heinz students for data analytics jobs and internships!'}

carnegiemellonece
caption:
{'text': 'Esther Bedoyan, a junior majoring ECE and biomedical engineering with a minor in Chinese studies, has received the prestigious 2021 Barry Goldwater Scholarship to encourage her pursuit of a research career.

Since the fall of 2020, Bedoyan has been conducting research in Dr. Maysam Chamanzar‚Äôs lab focusing on developing an adaptive frequency domain filtering technique that removes electrical interference from electrophysiology data.

‚ÄúI‚Äôve had a lot of fun with this project. I‚Äôve been able to independently develop this filtering technique and test its performance on real electrophysiology recordings collected from neural organoids and present my findings at multiple conferences and poster presentations,‚Äù Bedoyan said.

Upon graduation, she plans on completing the Integrated Masters Bachelor Program at CMU, then pursuing a Ph.D.

#goldwaterscholarship #engineer #cmuece @carnegiemellon @cmuengineering'}
